===Noun===
'''plus''' (''plural'' '''[[pluses]]''' or '''[[plusses]]''')
# A [[positive]] [[quantity]].
# An [[asset]] or [[useful]] [[addition]].
#: ''He is a real '''plus''' to the team.''
# {{arithmetic}} A [[plus sign]]: [[+]].

====Synonyms====
